## Analysis of top level Element[1]
This appears to be a call to a function (function selector 0x8014bad3),
which could be ```transferAll(address[],address)``` on the attack contract. The calldata matches
this function signature.

It appears to be: transfer from ```bb4cdb9cbd36b01bd1cbaebf2de08d9173bc095c```
to ```e183128b965ac347a5a082080cb9b6635faf9043```.
